NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._rewardPerSecond: The amount of Sushi to be distributed per second.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

extractRewards(uint256,address[],address.notice: Extract all rewards without withdrawing LP tokens

getNftIdsStaked(address).notice: View function to see the tokens staked by a given user.

getUpdatedAccTokenPerShare(address,addre.notice: Calculates an up to date value of accTokenPerShareAn updated value of accTokenPerShare is comitted to storage every time a new NFT is deposited, withdrawn or rewards are extracted

nftInfo(uint256).notice: Info of each NFT that is staked.

pendingToken(uint256,address).notice: View function to see pending Token

poolInfo(address,address).notice: Mapping to track the rewarder pool. baseToken -> rewardToken -> poolInfo

reclaimTokens(address,uint256,address).notice: Allows owner to reclaim/withdraw any tokens (including reward tokens) held by this contract

rewardRateLog(address,address,uint256).notice: Token => Reward Rate Updation history. baseToken -> rewardToken -> rewardsPerSecondEntry

setRewardPerSecond(address,address,uint2.notice: Sets the sushi per second to be distributed. Can only be called by the owner.
